    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been truly well-loved? I'm parting with my car, and it's in wonderful shape! It runs like a dream and has been kept super clean and tidy. It\u2019s the perfect match for someone who wants a solid, dependable vehicle that's ready for many more adventures. Come take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 32500.0,
