    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock, providing exceptional tactile feedback and cornering exit speeds. The chassis remains composed with a firm suspension tune, and critical preventative maintenance\u2014including a VANOS unit refresh and subframe reinforcement\u2014has been addressed to preserve structural integrity. While the exterior shows honest wear from spirited use, the powertrain exhibits excellent compression and immediate throttle response. A driver-focused machine that prioritizes analog engagement and peak atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
