    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle is a well-maintained example that strikes a perfect balance between performance and daily utility. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, professional touch-up on the driver-side door edge\u2014typical for a car of this age. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and odor-free. The upholstery shows light creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster, but all stitching remains intact, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in robust health; it has followed a strict preventative maintenance schedule, including a recent fluid service and a multi-point inspection. The engine runs quietly with no hesitation, and the suspension remains tight and responsive over bumps. It comes with two sets of keys and a documented service history. This is a dependable, honest car that looks great and drives even better.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
