      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and sophisticated design. This unit has been maintained with exacting standards, ensuring a dependable and smooth driving experience for its next owner. The exterior retains its professional luster, while the interior remains a testament to careful ownership. This is an exceptional opportunity to acquire a high-caliber automobile that balances performance with enduring value.",
