    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hi there! I\u2019m selling my absolute favorite ride and it\u2019s looking for a brand new home. This car has been so well-loved and is in really wonderful shape, ready to hit the road for all your upcoming adventures! It runs like a total dream and has been incredibly reliable for me. You\u2019re going to love how it handles\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
