    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and the factory M-Variable differential. The chassis remains composed with recent bushing refreshes and documented subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral G-loads. Maintenance is up to date, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and valve clearance adjustment. While showing honest signs of use, the mechanical synchronicity and throttle response through the individual throttle bodies remain razor-sharp. A true analog machine for the discerning pilot.",
